Path: godot/classes/class_editorselection.rst
Summary: Methods for managing node selection in the editor, including adding, removing, and retrieving selected nodes.

Method: add_node(node: Node) → void. Adds a node to the selection.
Method: clear() → void. Removes all nodes from the selection.
Method: get_selected_nodes() → Array[Node]. Returns all currently selected nodes.
Method: get_top_selected_nodes() → Array[Node]. Returns top-level selected nodes.
Method: get_transformable_selected_nodes() → Array[Node]. Returns nodes that can be transformed.
Method: remove_node(node: Node) → void. Removes a node from the selection.
